MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 820

DECLARING AS CIVIL RESERVATION FOR MULTI-PURPOSE DEVELOPMENT PROJECT SITES PURPOSES UNDER THE ADMINISTRATION OF THE PROVINCIAL GOVERNMENT OF IFUGAO, CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF PUBLIC DOMAIN LOCATED IN BRGY. POBLACION, MUNICIPALITY OF LAGAWE, PROVINCE OF IFUGAO, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I , GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby declare as civil reservation for multi-purpose development project sites purposes under the administration of the Provincial Government of Ifugao, certain parcels of land of public domain located in Brgy. Poblacion, Municipality of Lagawe, Province of Ifugao, Island of Luzon, containing an aggregate area of Sixteen Thousand Five Hundred Twenty Five (16,525) square meters, subject to private rights, if any there be, which parcels of land are more particularly described as follows:

Lot 1, Cad-996-D (PROVINCIAL CAPITOL)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 1, Cad-996-D, Lagawe Cadastre), situated at Brgy. Poblacion, Municipality of Lagawe, Province of Ifugao, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the W., along line 1-2 by Lagawe Proper Drive (10.00 m. wide); on the N., along line 2-3 by Abul Street (10.00 m. wide); on the E., along line 3-4 by Dotal Street (10.00 m. wide); and on the S., along line 4-1 by Don Bosco Street (10.00 m. wide).

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 64 deg. 18′ W., 96.77 meters from BLLM No. 1, Cad. 996-D, Lagawe Cadastre, thence:

96.94 m. to pt. 2;

74.73 m. to pt. 3;

95.98 m. to pt. 4;

75.05 m. to pt. of

beginning, containing an area of Seven Thousand Two Hundred Twenty Four (7,224) square meters, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 cm. Date of Survey: December 1, 1987 ‑ May 3, 1988 executed by Geodetic Engineer Dominador B. Aurelio and was approved on December 16, 1991.

Lot 2, Cad-996-D (TOWN PLAZA)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 2, Cad-996-D, Lagawe Cadastre), situated at Brgy. Poblacion, Municipality of Lagawe, Province of Ifugao, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the W., along lines 1-2-3-4 by Dotal Street (10.00 m. wide); on the N. along lines 4-5-6 by Abul Street (10.00 m. wide); on the NE., along lines 6-7-8 by Magdalene Route (10.00 m. wide); and on the S., along line 8-1 by Don Bosco Street (10.00 m. wide).

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 11 deg. 22′ W., 3.70 meters from BLLM No. 1, Cad. 996-D, Lagawe Cadastre, thence:

9.26 m. to pt. 2;

85.93 m. to pt. 3;

10.47 m. to pt. 4;

72.80 m. to pt. 5;

10.68 m. to pt. 6;

85.52 m. to pt. 7;

15.07 m. to pt. 8;

67.49 m. to pt. of

beginning, containing an area of Eight Thousand Six Hundred Twenty Two (8,622) square meters, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 cm. Date of Survey: December 1, 1987 ‑ May 3 1988 executed by Geodetic Engineer Dominador B. Aurelio and was approved on December 16, 1991.

Lot 8, Cad-996-D (MUNICIPAL HALL)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 8, Cad-996-D, Lagawe Cadastre), situated at Brgy. Poblacion, Municipality of Lagawe, Province of Ifugao, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the W., along line 1-2 by Magdalene Route (10.00 m. wide); on the NW., along line 2-3 by Lot 3, Cad-996-D; on the NE., along lines 3-4-5 by Lots 7, 9 and 1257, all of Cad-996-D; and on the SE., along line 5-1 by Lot 11, Cad-996-D, Lagawe Cadastre.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being N. 39 deg. 47’ E., 96.2 meters from BLLM No. 1, Cad. 996-D, Lagawe Cadastre, thence:

34.65 m. to pt. 2;

15.69 m. to pt. 3;

28.49 m. to pt. 4;

8.04 m. to pt. 5;

21.69 m. to pt. of

beginning, containing an area of Six Hundred Seventy Nine (679) square meters, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 cm. Date of Survey: December 1, 1987 ‑ May 3, 1988 executed by Geodetic Engineer Dominador B. Aurelio and was approved on December 16, 1991.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and cause the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 22nd day March in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

Source: CDAsia
